Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在風的節奏中推理漸漸清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的糾結也可以解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.13,0:00:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顧危險的追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與琴酒與伏特加的對決究竟鹿死誰手？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從被殺害的板倉先生的日記中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了與黑暗組織有關的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我和阿笠博士來到了板倉的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 伏特加卻打了電話過來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就在別墅裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回答我 板倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.81,0:02:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.42,0:02:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是抱歉 在黑暗中一時找不到電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.79,0:02:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就假扮板倉來引誘伏特加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約他在淩晨4點時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在施工中的賢橋車站的置物櫃那見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.85,0:02:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上鉤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在路上 博士的車子爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是只好攔下路過的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續向東京前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.49,0:03:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這兩個人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.74,0:03:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與黑暗組織的接觸（決死篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到了 兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要去的賢橋車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那裡不是還在施工嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那邊也沒電車坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家就住在車站附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.99,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是方便呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新一 真的要去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.00,0:03:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.45,0:03:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前還有件事情得解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不知道你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請不要在我車內講悄悄話好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.89,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不是叫你不要抽煙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.52,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不可以丟到窗外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丟到煙灰缸裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.67,0:04:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你把零錢和煙蒂放在一起不都髒掉了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再怎麼有錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做是會遭報應的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這兩個人就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶石搶匪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車根本不是這位大哥哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們可能是在山裡丟棄作案用的贓車後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在半路上搶路過的人的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車真正的主人是不抽煙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能方便付零錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把煙灰缸用來放零錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這位大哥哥沒有注意到這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來他發現裡面放了零錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是照樣當作煙灰缸來用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我們上車之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些零錢是因為我討厭他抽煙才故意放進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多的證據可以證明這輛車不是大哥哥的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不習慣在左邊開車的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常不自覺的開到能夠看清對面車子司機的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每當車子開到了馬路中間時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面的車子就會按喇叭警告他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒車的時候也不由自主地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反覆向視線不佳的左後方回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他不習慣用右手來換檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有在轉彎的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有打開方向燈反而打開雨刷對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.96,0:05:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他忘記進口車和國產車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制桿的位置是左右相反的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.53,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我要上車的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打開左邊的門就可以讓我上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妳卻要我從另一邊上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來聽了山村警官的一番話後 我終於明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為姐姐妳坐的地方下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.58,0:06:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有另一個剛才腿部被槍擊中的同伴所留下來的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該就躲在後車廂裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃避臨檢 躲在那裡避人耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他們為什麼還讓我們上車？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是一般的偷車賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會隨便讓人上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們故意讓我們上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了躲避臨檢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為車子裡要是載著老人和小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.00,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方就會以為我們是一家人而疏忽大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.93,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我已經發現這兩個人的身份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不僅搶了別人的車又做出這些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.96,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對就是正在逃亡的寶石搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 小弟弟你很聰明嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這麼小就那麼聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不好的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 既然被揭穿就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只好請你們跟我們一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.42,0:08:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是我們要在什麼地方解決這老頭和這小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.47,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這兩個人想去的賢橋車站怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方什麼人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在天亮前施工人員也不會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在臨檢的時候沒有對警察說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你已經知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是寶石搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想浪費時間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那裡把你們交給警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同乘一輛車的我們就要去錄口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就會耽誤我很重要的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們兩個我什麼時候都可以抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 口氣真硬啊 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣賞你這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.27,0:08:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 反正你說大話的時間也不長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時就算你哭著喊救命也不會饒了你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他短時間內是不會醒過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了我的麻醉針之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻醉針？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這小鬼到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.06,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種寶石店店員認不出的模型槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是騙不過我的眼睛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 小心旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.03,0:09:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是隨身足球腰帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特製的橡膠裡充滿氣就變成足球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種橡膠可以伸縮自如哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.97,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停充氣的話還可以變得更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士給警方打個電話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說抓到了寶石搶匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你真要到交易地點去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡離賢橋車站還有一段路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這裡來了警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙也不會停止交易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我擔心的不是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事我會用偵探徽章聯繫你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前不要靠近賢橋車站啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守住車站的周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.15,0:10:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一隻老鼠也不准放過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 板倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.76,0:12:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板倉這混蛋竟然還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支票？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.07,0:13:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和我們給板倉的金額不是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.22,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是委託板倉製作的那個軟體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.59,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 把錢留下還把東西也放在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是我 板倉應該還在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他抓到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.59,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.48,0:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進車站的只有醉漢和小鬼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！再給我搜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴酒？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易應該是在明天零點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.69,0:13:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙說明天不方便就改在這個時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.03,0:14:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是那傢伙發電子郵件約定的時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是 時間是我們定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在原來的別墅收了郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說因為大雪停電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就直接用電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒找到那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們要的軟體到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙心臟不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.48,0:14:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們不殺他他遲早會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這個軟體為什麼會用膠帶固定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.38,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了取得你的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.35,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為帶著手套是撕不下膠帶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對方不出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會心神不安的點上香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要查查你的唾液就能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 連我們的老巢都想要揪出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 盒子裡有發信器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真是只狡猾的狐狸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板倉這個混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是板倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫差過大會刺激交感神經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.59,0:15:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加大心臟的負荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,患有心臟病的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.69,0:15:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會在暴風雪中跑到群馬的別墅裡去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.22,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼和我通電話的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是那傢伙雇的什麼人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是出了一點紕漏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個盒子上的指紋雖然擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是盒子還是溫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.93,0:16:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還在這附近窺視著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來會被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 剩下的只有那裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.64,0:16:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的狐狸現在變成籠中的老鼠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.92,0:17:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.86,0:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 一個大人怎麼會藏在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 大概是變裝逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定已經通知警方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你是說板倉雇的那個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你要小心了 別再有下次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.14,0:18:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得有人在調查我們組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是像偵探一樣的狐狸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？要不要去追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 還太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們假裝逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們到底想要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓灰原製作奇怪的藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又讓板倉開發軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和藥沒什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.05,0:19:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了人類而放棄研發的軟體到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿笠博士 您的功勞真不小啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然您已經累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還得麻煩您去錄個口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？千葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是犯人的傷勢問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.97,0:19:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？腳步聲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人走過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…身體動彈不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.92,0:21:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？灰原？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.75,0:21:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.03,0:21:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳又為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和博士都沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用追蹤眼鏡找到這裡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經早上了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.12,0:22:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹 找到妳朋友了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.32,0:22:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.37,0:22:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快點出去吧 別妨礙我們施工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.53,0:22:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 工藤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.13,0:22:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來因為缺氧在箱子裡失去知覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.97,0:22:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你到底在那裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.22,0:22:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…因為好久沒睡…就在那裡打了個盹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這就是回答嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.35,0:22:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…應該算吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.54,0:22:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.88,0:23:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士他怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事 現在應該和警方在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.98,0:23:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一條新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下午5點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.29,0:23:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在米花大酒店發現一具男性屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.98,0:23:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是著名的CG設計師板倉卓 45歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.88,0:23:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.04,0:23:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.36,0:23:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.76,0:23:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.86,0:23:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黃鶯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.70,0:23:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊就聽得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.30,0:24:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是靜山先生的鳥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話 那莫非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.90,0:24:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.20,0:24:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽光普照的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.60,0:24:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃鶯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月七日播出電影版 貝克街的亡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影系列從四月十四日再續播哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:30.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海風中感覺到你的氣息 銀色的波浪消除了二人的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.73,0:00:43.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣讓時間停止吧 遠遠看去藐小的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.29,0:00:53.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法再分離 與你約定在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀的季節中得來不易的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.09,0:01:08.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再迷惘 相信我的眼神 風的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.31,0:01:15.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在溢滿的不安中隱藏淚水的昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.98,0:01:25.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠的回憶現在終於可以說出 風的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.77,0:20:09.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到你的電話聲 如此堅強的我也會哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.78,0:20:17.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管彼此傷害對方 但是還是想見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.17,0:20:22.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使結局終究令人厭惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.04,0:20:30.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對於給我的回答覺得為難吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.93,0:20:38.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起你那無法掩藏的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.01,0:20:42.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…I miss you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.64,0:20:56.36,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想明天 希望能夠相信 即使路途坎坷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.62,0:21:05.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想明天 你的全部 希望能夠見到你
